          </div>
          <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer home-llm-cards w-container">
            <img src="/images/pages/power-than-llm_optimized-rag.svg" loading="lazy" width="60" height="60" alt=""/>
            <div class="home-card-content">
              <h3 class="card-h">Optimize Accuracy with Your Knowledge</h3>
              <p>AI can't always identify which invoice number is most relevant to your system - but YOU can! Provide samples to teach the AI which invoice numbers to extract for each merchant.</p>
