              <p>Continuously fine-tune LLMs using real-world feedback to achieve higher accuracy and reliability.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer home-llm-cards w-container">
            <img src="/images/pages/power-than-llm_mix-multiple.svg" loading="lazy" width="60" height="60" alt=""/>
            <div class="home-card-content">
              <h3 class="card-h">Mix Multiple Models for Different Document Types</h3>
              <p>Combine specialized models to handle diverse document types seamlessly, ensuring maximum efficiency.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
